snippet.title: Shutokou Battle '97, 1997 -Sega Saturn Japanese Import Gameplay
snippet.description: Further down the import Rabbit hole we go with this 3D racer which didn't grace PAL territories, this is the 1997 update, so surely it's got to be a decent game hasn't it....? Well... Judge for yourself and head over to read my review at https://saturnimportchannel.wordpress.com
